descriptions.direction: Located in Velavaru, Angsana Velavaru is near the beach. Meedhoo Harbour and Vommuli Pier are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Meedhuffushi Island Beach and Kandima Beach. Take an opportunity to explore the area for water adventures such as windsurfing.
